{"tid":1400441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗人麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:14:49.000Z","uid":232917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b943bb8e97570aa9f6ede896fc83058c440472af","tid":1400441,"uid":232917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:55:53.000Z","msg":"Sorry呀做咗標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓各位住元朗嘅巴絲有冇執到個棗紅色嘅卡片套<br />\n入面有我張身份證同八達通 同埋有迪士尼全年證<br />\n希望各位可以幫我手睇吓有冇人執到<br />\n我其實想報失不過一嚟班狗唔做嘢二嚟我驚佢見我大專生會上我屋企查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫吓手呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cded2be9ed3b210d1c1bb19dc098f6a7c8bee8c3","tid":1400441,"uid":232917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人"},{"pid":"83751ebb67bbfb63b7516c2ae47a7a4b8a617877","tid":1400441,"uid":232917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"d9326b5ad7988c11f965e6b7f67ec80a7818c42d","tid":1400441,"uid":232917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"幫手"},{"pid":"37652af8ed7fdb4d49b978a7582a75773e61e906","tid":1400441,"uid":232917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"搵吓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa7ae3ab64ea5c5f73ea0841cf1fcbf3e62dcd9","tid":1400441,"uid":46380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔講幾時同邊度掉點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0478d09fb4eb16a4362849bd5f26